			<article id="post-1279" class="post-1279 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-uncategorized tag-canada tag-canada-employment-immigration tag-canada-immigration tag-canada-immigration-department tag-canada-immigration-lawyer tag-canada-immigration-skilled-worker tag-canada-visa tag-canadian-immigration tag-canadian-immigration-attorney tag-canadian-immigration-department tag-canadian-immigration-skilled-worker tag-express-entry tag-federal-application tag-immigration tag-immigration-and-refugee-protection-act tag-immigration-minister tag-online-express-entry-profile tag-permanent-residence tag-permanent-residence-card tag-permanent-residency">

